    content: "<p>Hi all, NYC Philanthropy here.<br> <a href=\"https://explorer.livepeer.org/accounts/0xb5164D6B780786338C52F4787ABba0e4a371Af4d/delegating\" target=\"_blank\">NYC Philanthropy Node on Livepeer Explorer</a></p> <p>Our current LPT Reward/ETH Fee Cuts are: 50%/50%</p> <p>This node has pledged at least 30% of this node’s Total ETH Fee earnings to be directed towards philanthropic efforts. Please keep updated on the donations at <a href=\"http://nycphilanthropy.com\" target=\"_blank\">nycphilanthropy.com</a></p>",
